1. *Brzi* voz ide za Beograd. (*Fast* train is going to Belgrade.)
2. Moramo biti *brzi* ako želimo stići na vreme. (We need to be *fast* if we want to arrive on time.)
3. On je *brži* trčao od mene. (He ran *faster* than me.)
4. *Brzi* rast tehnologije je promenio način na koji živimo. (*Fast* technological growth has changed the way we live.)
5. Moram *brzo* da završim ovaj posao. (I need to finish this job *quickly*.)
6. *Brzi* odgovor na pitanje mi je pomogao da pobedim. (*Quick* response to the question helped me win.)
7. *Brže-bolje* smo krenuli na put. (We set off on the journey *hurriedly*.)
8. *Brzi* automobili su opasni na cesti. (*Fast* cars are dangerous on the road.)
9. Nisam mogao da uhvatim *brzi* voz koji sam planirao. (I couldn't catch the *express* train that I planned.)
10. Danas sam bio *brži* nego juče. (Today I was *faster* than yesterday.)